<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product Landing Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .hero {
            background: url('https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?technology') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        .testimonials {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        .cta {
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="hero">
        <div>
            <h1>Discover Our Amazing Products</h1>
            <p>High-quality, innovative, and designed just for you.</p>
            <a href="#features" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Explore Now</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="features" class="container text-center feature">
        <h2>Why Choose Our Products?</h2>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h4>Premium Quality</h4>
                <p>Our products are made from the best materials.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h4>Affordable Prices</h4>
                <p>Get the best value for your money.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h4>Fast Shipping</h4>
                <p>We deliver your products quickly and safely.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials text-center">
        <h2>What Our Customers Say</h2>
        <p>"This is the best product I have ever purchased!" - Jane Doe</p>
        <p>"Amazing quality and excellent customer service." - John Smith</p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
        <h2>Get Yours Today!</h2>
        <p>Don't miss out on our exclusive offers.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Shop Now</a>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
